{
  "stem": "20035.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he had the biggest pleasure of kicking and punching, and-- and-- and-- and-- and any kind of brutality, whatever he could do to anybody.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And you know, the-- the [GERMAN], which means Jew pig, that was the greeting of hello, I love you.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was the nicest, what he could say.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But besides of-- of us, on the other side of the railroad track, there was a huge POW camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Well, the POW camp had French, English, and Russian soldiers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Not one American uniform that we have seen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They were working inside, in the factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were never allowed into the factory.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So the only contact, what we had, that we took from the railroad to the factory, anything, whatever had to be brought there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "By the way, no mechanized equipment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Everything is physical.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they are the one who brought it in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they worked us as-- we as human machines.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So that was our only contact with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But there are the-- once we started, and we started to work there, our-- what you have to understand, that we went through, already, four, three, four, five, six months, without any kind of whatsoever what we know hygiene, or what-- what-- what-- what existed to-- to wash your face, wash your clothes.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "There's no such a thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It's the same clothes, the same shoes, the same shirts and the same pants and jacket.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All over.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From-- from day one in Auschwitz, there is nothing else but a latrine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And latrine and no such a thing as toilet paper.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "No such thing as a soap or water or toothbrush or toothpaste or comb, or-- comb wasn't necessarily real.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the basic idea was that once a month, they kept your hair on a brush-cut basis.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
